OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FRain across central and eastern
OL,6,Fareas soon clearing. Showers following
OL,7,Ffor most, these heavy in Northern
OL,8,FIreland and western Scotland, with a
OL,9,Frisk of hail and thunder. Windy for
OL,10,Fall with coastal gales in the west.
OL,11,FTemperatures near average.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FFurther blustery showers with
OL,14,Flonger spells of rain likely across
OL,15,Fthe northwest. However some eastern
OL,16,Fcounties will remain dry with clear
OL,17,Fspells. Windy with coastal gales in
OL,18,Fthe northwest.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
