OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CSunday:FAnother day of sunny spells
OL,6,Fand blustery showers, a continued risk
OL,7,Fof hail and thunder, particularly in
OL,8,Fthe north and west of the country.
OL,9,FFeeling chilly with strong gusty winds.
